	<header class="page-header">
		<h1 class="page-title">Careers</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><img class="alignright wp-image-283 size-large" src="http://www.sbti.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/main-join-us-1030x474.png" alt="Join Our Team" width="750" height="345" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Stonebridge is looking for talented individuals to join our team. We&#8217;re looking for oil and gas experts and technology consultants driven to move beyond the status quo, professionally and personally. Take a look at our career opportunities. If you think you have what it takes, we&#8217;d love to hear from you.</p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/enerhub-bi-technical-lead/"><strong>EnerHub BI Technical Lead</strong></a></p>
<p>As the EnerHub BI Technical Lead, you will be expected to provide leadership in product development and technical delivery for Stonebridge Consulting’s flagship BI offering, EnerHub. Your focus will be on originating, managing, and delivering client engagements throughout the country, but primarily in our main geographies: Houston, Oklahoma City, Dallas, Pittsburgh, Tulsa, and Denver. <a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/enerhub-bi-technical-lead/">Learn More ::</a></p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/managing-director/">Managing Director</a></strong></p>
<p>The Managing Director role is a leadership position focused on originating, managing and delivering client engagements throughout the country but primarily in our main geographies: Houston, Oklahoma City, Dallas, Pittsburgh, Tulsa, and Denver. In this role, a Managing Director provides leadership and guidance in developing and positioning Stonebridge’s core offerings: Advisory Services, Technology Services, and Managed Services. <a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/managing-director/">Learn More ::</a></p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/business-intelligence/"><strong>Business Intelligence/Data Warehousing Consultant</strong></a></p>
<p>We are currently seeking experienced Microsoft Business Intelligence/Data Warehouse Consultants with exceptional consulting skills and the ability to articulate technical concepts to mixed audiences. These positions are based out of our Houston, Dallas, Oklahoma City and Tulsa offices. Candidates may be located anywhere in the U.S. but willing to relocate or travel up to 50%.  <a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/business-intelligence/">Learn More ::</a></p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/advisory-consultant/"><strong>Advisory Consultant</strong></a></p>
<p>The Advisory Consultant is responsible for displaying a high level of competency in consulting, oil and gas business acumen, business development, and technical knowledge. You are responsible for working alongside clients and providing strategic guidance on business processes and IT capabilities. This ranges from identifying and developing client and market growth opportunities that are focused on the clients’ business strategies to improving business value through process-relevant systems and architecture.  <a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/advisory-consultant/">Learn More ::</a></p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a title="Enterprise Content Management Consultants" href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/enterprise-content-management-consultants/"><strong>Enterprise Content Management Consultants</strong></a></p>
<p>We are currently seeking experienced Microsoft SharePoint Developers, Architects and ECM/RM Consultants with exceptional consulting skills and the ability to articulate technical concepts to mixed audiences. Consultants will assess SharePoint readiness, perform plan migrations and upgrades, and develop custom applications for our clients. These positions are based out of our Houston, Dallas, Oklahoma City and Tulsa offices. Candidates may be located anywhere in the U.S. but willing to relocate or travel up to 50%.  <a title="Enterprise Content Management Consultants" href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/enterprise-content-management-consultants/">Learn More ::</a></p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/sharepoint-architect/"><strong>SharePoint Architect</strong></a></p>
<p>We are currently seeking experienced Microsoft SharePoint Developers, Architects and ECM Consultants with exceptional consulting skills and the ability to articulate technical concepts to mixed audiences. Consultants will assess SharePoint readiness, perform plan migrations and upgrades, and develop custom applications for our clients. These positions are based out of our Houston, Dallas, Oklahoma City and Tulsa offices. Candidates may be located anywhere in the U.S. but willing to relocate or travel up to 50%.  <a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/sharepoint-architect/">Learn More ::</a></p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/sharepoint-developer/"><strong>SharePoint Developer</strong></a></p>
<p>We are currently seeking experienced Microsoft SharePoint Developers, Architects and ECM/RM Consultants with exceptional consulting skills and the ability to articulate technical concepts to mixed audiences. Consultants will assess SharePoint readiness, perform plan migrations and upgrades, and develop custom applications for our clients. These positions are based out of our Houston, Dallas, Oklahoma City and Tulsa offices. Candidates may be located anywhere in the U.S. but willing to relocate or travel up to 50%.  <a href="http://www.sbti.com/careers/sharepoint-developer/">Learn More ::</a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
